    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car has been pampered since day one\u2014always kept in the garage, strictly hand-washed, and honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even more stunning in person. If you\u2019ve been searching for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
