    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s pristine inside and out and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and perfectly kept, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
