    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 power plant. This example delivers a visceral 8,400 RPM redline paired with a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is superlative, with a documented service history addressing critical rod bearing tolerances and throttle actuators. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a Variable M Differential Lock, ensuring optimal lateral grip and power delivery. The exterior retains its original factory paint depth and clarity, while the interior leather maintains its matte finish and structural bolster integrity. A collector-quality specimen offering telepathic steering feedback and an unadulterated naturally aspirated soundtrack.",
